title: Search for up to four people swept down Waikato River near Lake Taupo | Stuff.co.nz
text:
Search for up to four people swept down Waikato River near Lake Taupo Last updated 13:31, February 6 2017 MATT SHAND/FAIRFAX NZ 
Police are searching for four people who were swept down the Waikato River near Taupo. 
Up to four people have been swept down Waikato River near Taupo. 
Police are actively searching the area and a helicopter has joined the search. 
The people were reported missing shortly after noon. 
More soon.
